shows.title: 10 Buildings That Changed America
shows.overview: 10 Buildings That Changed America tells the stories of ten influential works of architecture, the people who imagined them, and the way these landmarks ushered in innovative cultural shifts throughout our society. These 10 Buildings represent architects who dared to strike out on their own and design radical new types of buildings that permanently altered our environmental and cultural landscape.

shows.title: 10 Days in a Madhouse
shows.overview: In 1887, reporter Nellie Bly feigns mental illness and works undercover to expose abuse, corruption, and murder at a notorious women’s insane asylum.

shows.title: 100 Missions Surviving Vietnam
shows.overview: Track the stories of the pilots of Vietnam's Operation Rolling Thunder and their race to survive their 100-mission goal.

shows.title: 101 Inventions That Changed The World
shows.overview: Take a closer look at the inventions that have transformed our lives far beyond our homes (the steam engine), our planet (the telescope) and our wildest dreams (the Internet).

shows.title: 102 Minutes That Changed America
shows.overview: The terror of 9/11 is chronicled in real time utilizing footage from personal camcorders, police and fire department recordings, and in-the-moment commentary from first responders and witnesses.

shows.title: 9/11: Stories from the City
shows.overview: Twenty years on, listen to some of the incredible first-hand stories in this emotional reflection on one of the darkest days in American history.

shows.title: 12 Mighty Orphans
shows.overview: Rusty Russell coaches football at an orphanage in Fort Worth, Texas, during the Great Depression.

shows.title: 12 Strong
shows.overview: Set in the harrowing days following 9/11, an elite team of Green Berets joins forces with an Afghan general to take control of a Taliban stronghold.

shows.title: 12 Years a Slave
shows.overview: Based on an incredible true story of Solomon Northup who was abducted and sold into slavery during pre-Civil War United States. Facing cruelty as well as unexpected kindnesses, Solomon struggles not only to stay alive, but to retain his dignity.

shows.title: 13 Hours: The Secret Soldiers of Benghazi
shows.overview: This is the gripping true story of six elite ex-military ops assigned to protect the CIA who fought back against all odds when terrorists attacked a U.S. diplomatic compound on 9/11/2012.
shows.originalTitle: 13 Hours: The Secret Soldiers of Benghazi

shows.title: 13th
shows.overview: In this thought-provoking documentary, scholars, activists and politicians analyze the criminalization of African Americans and the U.S. prison boom.

shows.title: 141 A.D. Mission in Dacia
shows.overview: When a deadly epidemic threatens to run rampant through the Roman Empire, four soldiers are sent beyond its borders in search of a rumored cure.

shows.title: 15 Février 1839
shows.overview: French Canadians face execution after a revolt against British bureaucrats in Quebec.

shows.title: 16 Acres
shows.overview: Interests collide at Ground Zero in the decade following 9/11.

shows.title: 16 Photographs at Ohrdruf
shows.overview: A filmmaker sets out with a handful of his grandfather’s photos to reveal a family secret and tell of the soldiers who uncovered the Holocaust
Haunted by chemical attacks that claimed the lives of his family, a persecuted Kurdish sniper flees his homeland in search of a better life in the UK.
As the Inquisition's persecution of Portuguese Jews puts his family and community in danger, António Álvares outlines an escape plan.

shows.title: 17 Miracles
shows.overview: In 1857, Mormon pioneers embark on an arduous trek, pushing their handcarts across the plains and finding sustenance in a series of miracles.
Follows the second Continental Congress’ attempt to meet demands of creating a new government during its struggle for independence from the British.

shows.title: 1812. Ballad of the Uhlans
shows.overview: On the eve before the decisive Battle of Borodino during Napoleon's 1812 invasion of Russia, a French secret agent steals the Russian command plan.
